        <detaileddescription>
<para>Gets the option information for all options.</para>
<para>The dict has the full option names as keys and option metadata dicts as detailed at |nvim_get_option_info2()|.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>|nvim_get_commands()|</para>
</simplesect>
